import React, { Component } from 'react' import {formateDate} from '../../utils/dateUtils' import memoryUtils from '../../utils/memoryUtils' import './index.less' /** * 头部显示区域 */ export default class Header extends Component { state = { currentTime: formateDate(Date.now()), //当前时间的字符串格式 } render() { const {currentTime} =this.state const username = memoryUtils.user.username return (
当前用户：{username} 退出
首页
{currentTime} 晴天
) } }
